myblog v1 plans:
=================
db:
----
user - first_name, last_name, email, password, created_at
role - [use fields from demo app] (subscriber, admin)
users_roles - [use from demo app]

pages:
-----
homepage, profile page

functionalities:
-------
user signup, user login, user logout, user specific pages (profile)

myblog v2 plans:
===============
db:
-----
post - id, title, content, user_id, created_at, updated_at, status

pages:
-----
posts, add post, edit post

functionalities:
--------
- user can create post
- user can edit post
- user can view all his posts and delete posts from the list posts page
